1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,770
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:01,770 --> 00:00:03,480
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,110
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:22,660
Joo Ha Neul, hurry up and get here.

5
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:29,470
I have a debt to collect.

6
00:00:35,210 --> 00:00:36,610
(Episode 99)

7
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:48,710
Se Mi!

8
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:51,780
Se Mi.

9
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:53,750
Se Mi.

10
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:17,140
What is it? Is something wrong?

11
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:20,210
I think something's happened
to Se Mi.

12
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,810
Ha Neul is on his way to her now.

13
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:25,550
What? Where is she?

14
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,130
Where are you?

15
00:02:36,790 --> 00:02:37,800
It's me.

16
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:40,830
Your one and only love,
Jin Tae Seok.

17
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:43,700
Don't tell me you have Se Mi...

18
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:46,800
Yes, she's with me.

19
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,940
You didn't do anything to her,
did you?

20
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,510
Why did you have to mess with me?

21
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,780
None of this would've happened...

22
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:57,580
if you hadn't stolen my account
and driven me to the edge.

23
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,790
Jin Tae Seok, where is Se Mi?

24
00:03:02,950 --> 00:03:05,860
Jin Tae Seok took Se Mi?

25
00:03:07,330 --> 00:03:09,830
See for yourself.
Our daughter is perfectly fine.

26
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,800
Jin Tae Seok!

27
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,610
And one more thing.

28
00:03:21,170 --> 00:03:22,610
I didn't want Se Mi to be lonely,

29
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:25,140
so I invited the man she loves,
Joo Ha Neul, to join her.

30
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:27,810
- I'll send them off together.
- Se Mi!

31
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:31,150
Chairman Joo! Se Mi!

32
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:36,820
You and Gong Nan Sook betrayed me.
This is just payback, isn't it?

33
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,120
See this?

34
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:43,430
If you don't spit out the password
to the Swiss account right now,

35
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:46,100
you'll never see these kids again.

36
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,530
Jin Tae Seok!

37
00:03:47,730 --> 00:03:49,130
I'll give you exactly 30 minutes.

38
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:51,370
And tell Gong Nan Sook.

39
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,270
Tell her to cough up
all the money she stole.

40
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,610
You two seem to be
on the same wavelength.

41
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:02,780
Jin Tae Seok!

42
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:08,790
Mom, we have to find
Se Mi right away.

43
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:10,250
And Ha Neul, too.

44
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:20,130
What are we going to do?

45
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,130
He's lost his mind.

46
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:37,080
Mom, please, pull yourself together.

47
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,080
What are we going to do?

48
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,420
What are we going to do about Se Mi?

49
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:41,790
What do we do?

50
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,520
Give the Swiss account...

51
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:46,560
to Jin Tae Seok.

52
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:53,030
- What?
- Se Mi and Ha Neul come first.

53
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:58,440
You're right.

54
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,810
Have you made up your mind?

55
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,880
I'll send you...

56
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,680
the Swiss account password now.

57
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:11,780
Just let Se Mi and Chairman Joo go.

58
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:13,220
The password first.

59
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:28,570
Go ahead and check.

60
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:35,710
I've confirmed it.

61
00:05:35,910 --> 00:05:38,880
Then let Se Mi and Chairman Joo go!

62
00:05:41,910 --> 00:05:43,110
Sorry, Hye Ra.

63
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,790
Jin Tae Seok!

64
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,590
He just hung up.

65
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:53,620
We have to go now.
I know the address.

66
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:58,400
Right. Wait.
I have to tell Gong Nan Sook.

67
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:02,500
What? Jin Tae Seok has
Ha Neul and Se Mi?

68
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:03,670
Where are they?

69
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:07,340
First, wire the money you took back.

70
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,910
Jin Tae Seok has lost his mind.

71
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:10,580
He's threatening to set
the place on fire.

72
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,340
Jin Tae Seok, that bastard.

73
00:06:28,690 --> 00:06:32,230
Joo Ha Neul really is
your Achilles' heel, Gong Nan Sook.

74
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,970
I coughed it all up.

75
00:06:36,970 --> 00:06:39,400
The money was transferred
to your Swiss account.

76
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:43,210
Hold on. Let me check first.

77
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:54,390
Finally, everything's back
to how it should be.

78
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:58,990
Jin Tae Seok, if you dare touch
a single hair on my Ha Neul's head,

79
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:02,830
I will bury you alive.

80
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,900
And then I'll dig you up
over and over again...

81
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:08,230
and rip out your guts
and chew them to pieces.

82
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:09,570
Calm down.

83
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:14,710
You actually coughed up the money
you said you never would.

84
00:07:15,070 --> 00:07:17,010
So of course,
I have to let Joo Ha Neul go.

85
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:19,580
Stay where you are. I'm on my way.

86
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,680
Stop.

87
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:24,520
If you so much as show
your face here,

88
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,880
I'll burn this place to the ground.

89
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:29,220
Hye Ra will come running.

90
00:07:29,650 --> 00:07:32,920
Gong Nan Sook,
don't you dare move a muscle.

91
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,230
You know I've lost my mind
right now, right?

92
00:07:36,030 --> 00:07:37,400
So you'd better take me seriously.

93
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:47,740
Don't go.
He said he'd set the place on fire.

94
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:50,940
But Ha Neul's been captured.
How can I possibly stay here?

95
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:53,010
Get a hold of yourself!

96
00:07:53,210 --> 00:07:54,350
Grandma.

97
00:07:54,850 --> 00:07:56,680
Is Ha Neul going to be okay?

98
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,450
Nothing bad will happen, right?

99
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:02,720
Our sweet boy.

100
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:05,390
A child more precious than any other.

101
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,460
I will protect him.

102
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,200
Goodness...

103
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:12,700
Chairman Gong!

104
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:53,910
My dear Se Mi.

105
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:57,480
You know how much
Daddy loves you, right?

106
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,580
I'm so sorry for hurting you.

107
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:03,580
In time,

108
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,920
you'll understand my reasons.

109
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,750
Just hang in there
a little longer, Se Mi.

110
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:40,890
Se Mi...

111
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:42,950
Ha Neul.

112
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,920
Is this...

113
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:46,720
a dream?

114
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,100
How could my own father
do this to me?

115
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,800
How could he?

116
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:56,300
Se Mi,

117
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:58,270
pull yourself together.

118
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:00,500
We have to get out of here now.

119
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,450
Se Mi!

120
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,820
Ha Neul, are you okay?

121
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:19,260
Se Mi. Are you okay?

122
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:20,730
Mom.

123
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,860
Goodness...

124
00:10:25,730 --> 00:10:26,860
Let's hurry.

125
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:28,700
I have something urgent
to take care of.

126
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,410
Let's go.

127
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:44,380
My dad tried to start a fire.

128
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,920
My poor Se Mi.

129
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,620
Jin Tae Seok is worse
than an animal...

130
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:57,460
for hurting Se Mi,
whom he cherished so much.

131
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:14,110
Chairman Joo. Are you all right?

132
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,450
Yes, I made it out safely.
You must have been worried.

133
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,550
Thankfully,
nothing serious happened.

134
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:21,390
And how is my mother?

135
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:24,060
Ha Neul!

136
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,560
Goodness, Ha Neul!

137
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:28,290
Are you okay? Thank goodness.

138
00:11:28,430 --> 00:11:31,460
- Thank goodness.
- I'm fine, so please get some rest.

139
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:34,700
I'm okay now. What a relief.

140
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,270
You must be hungry.
Let's get you something to eat.

141
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,370
I have something more important
to take care of first.

142
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:59,560
Why aren't you answering my calls,
Manager Gu?

143
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:08,370
Please, can you just tell me
where Se Hoon is?

144
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:12,700
Manager Gu, I'm begging you.

145
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:20,180
Former Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon
is in a psychiatric hospital.

146
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,310
My goodness.

147
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,580
Jin Tae Seok went after
Director Jin Se Mi, too?

148
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:32,850
What kind of monster is he?

149
00:13:37,190 --> 00:13:38,390
Pace yourself.

150
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,330
Let's just drink ourselves
to death tonight.

151
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:43,090
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

152
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,070
Ki Beom.

153
00:13:48,930 --> 00:13:51,570
You'll protect Jung Won, won't you?

154
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:17,490
Yes, Chairman Joo, I'm fine.
What's going on?

155
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:24,870
Why did you come all the way here?
You can't be feeling well.

156
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:28,110
We need to get back the account
that Jin Tae Seok stole.

157
00:14:30,210 --> 00:14:32,840
Secretary Yoon, there's something
I need you to do.

158
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,250
Tell me what you need.

159
00:14:44,090 --> 00:14:45,590
Would you like a cup of tea?

160
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:46,920
Where's Se Mi?

161
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,160
She's asleep.
We gave her a sedative.

162
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:54,270
My poor, sweet Se Mi.
She must have been so traumatized.

163
00:14:56,130 --> 00:14:59,000
Se Mi should have calmed down
by now.

164
00:14:59,470 --> 00:15:00,870
You should probably go see her...

165
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:16,220
Here's the laptop.
You can get to work right away.

166
00:15:16,290 --> 00:15:17,350
Thank you, Secretary Yoon.

167
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:22,630
I'll keep watch and let you know
if anything happens.

168
00:15:22,730 --> 00:15:23,730
Thank you.

169
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,460
When Se Mi gets older,

170
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:00,430
she'll understand me.

171
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,420
What is this?

172
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,490
Where's all the money?

173
00:16:29,490 --> 00:16:30,590
Han Hye Ra!

174
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:33,160
Did you steal all the money
in the Swiss account again?

175
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,530
Is that really what's important
right now?

176
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,470
How dare you...

177
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:42,310
How dare you pull a stunt
like that on Se Mi?

178
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:44,210
I never meant any harm to Se Mi.

179
00:16:44,410 --> 00:16:47,040
It was the only way
to teach you a lesson!

180
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:48,310
Jin Tae Seok.

181
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:53,120
To think a father would gamble
with his daughters' lives...

182
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,820
is absolutely sickening!

183
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:59,590
Han Hye Ra, please,
just give me the money back.

184
00:17:00,290 --> 00:17:02,160
Just give it now!

185
00:17:03,990 --> 00:17:06,000
Stop this and get out!

186
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,130
You disgust me!

187
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:09,770
I said give me the money back now!

188
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,270
Please!

189
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,410
Welcome, Jin Jung Won.
Or should I say,

190
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:24,050
Chief Director Cha Jung Won.

191
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,480
I'm surprised you reached out first.

192
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:29,020
You wired the other two million.

193
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:31,690
You're a woman of your word,

194
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:34,630
so I wanted to see you again.

195
00:17:34,890 --> 00:17:36,590
You must have something you want.

196
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:40,960
From Jin Tae Seok's slush fund's list,

197
00:17:42,030 --> 00:17:44,600
- leave the old man out of it.
- And if I agree to that,

198
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:48,340
what's in it for me?

199
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:51,580
The old man is prepared
to grant you permission...

200
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:55,050
to get rid of Jin Tae Seok.

201
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:18,240
Kim Ji Hwan, answer your phone!

202
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:22,670
I'm not going down alone.
I refuse to!

203
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:28,380
(Kunhyang Group)

204
00:18:28,450 --> 00:18:30,850
(Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

205
00:18:35,850 --> 00:18:39,260
Today, we need to make Jin Tae Seok
utterly powerless.

206
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:41,960
Let's go and give a grand finale.

207
00:18:45,330 --> 00:18:47,000
Let's go. It's time to end this.

208
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:58,480
(Establishment and Appointment of
Kunhyang Group Emergency Committee)

209
00:18:58,580 --> 00:19:00,440
The company is facing
its greatest crisis ever.

210
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,910
Because of
the rooftop incident footage,

211
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:05,880
public opinion has hit
an all-time low.

212
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:08,190
And faith in our leadership
is wavering.

213
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:12,420
As an advisor,
I would like to make a proposal.

214
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:14,590
That a new chairman
of the emergency committee...

215
00:19:15,290 --> 00:19:16,930
must be appointed.

216
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:18,100
I agree.

217
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:20,630
Kunhyang Group's power structure
needs to be re-examined now.

218
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:21,900
You're the problem.

219
00:19:22,530 --> 00:19:25,500
The contacts I built for decades
have turned their backs on Kunhyang.

220
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:28,170
Jin Tae Seok, you're the problem.

221
00:19:28,370 --> 00:19:31,070
Your very name
is poison to this company!

222
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,540
Gong Nan Sook! Do you think
you can just say whatever you want?

223
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:36,410
Kunhyang is mine.
I'm the one who built this company!

224
00:19:37,210 --> 00:19:38,820
An emergency committee? Fine.

225
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:41,050
I'll be the chairman myself.

226
00:19:41,050 --> 00:19:42,720
Don't be ridiculous.

227
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:46,220
Right now, the public
is holding you accountable.

228
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:51,230
As of now, the only one qualified
to be the committee's chairman...

229
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:53,330
is Chief Director Jin Jung Won,

230
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:55,570
the one you named your successor.

231
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:57,330
What on earth are you saying?

232
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,570
(Establishment and Appointment of
Kunhyang Group Emergency Committee)

233
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:03,070
Stabilizing the company
should be our first priority.

234
00:20:03,210 --> 00:20:05,540
I can't support
the Honorary Chairman any longer.

235
00:20:05,540 --> 00:20:07,040
There are no grounds to.

236
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:11,580
This is a conspiracy
to force me out.

237
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:13,980
Don't waver. I'm Jin Tae Seok!

238
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:18,090
Chief Director Jin Jung Won.

239
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:21,660
You don't have what it takes
to run this company yet.

240
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:24,330
Give me the chairman position
for now.

241
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:33,940
Honorary Chairman, you're the one
who appointed me as your successor.

242
00:20:36,610 --> 00:20:38,640
If you go back on your word
so easily,

243
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:40,980
how can anyone trust you,
Honorary Chairman?

244
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:43,910
I...

245
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:46,220
am qualified.

246
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:00,530
You're not dead yet?

247
00:21:09,140 --> 00:21:11,880
Goodness.
What in the world is he doing?

248
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,280
He's trying to kill him, right?

249
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:18,850
- How...
- Jin Jung Won...

250
00:21:18,850 --> 00:21:20,120
Twenty five years ago,

251
00:21:21,020 --> 00:21:23,850
you framed my father, Cha Ki Beom,
and ruined his life.

252
00:21:24,490 --> 00:21:25,560
And in the end,

253
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:28,930
you stomped the last breath
out of him.

254
00:21:29,530 --> 00:21:32,430
That's horrific. He's a monster.

255
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,830
That's terrifying.

256
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,330
It's all doctored!

257
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:39,570
I said it was "doctored" too.

258
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:44,340
With respect to the rooftop video
that was posted online,

259
00:21:44,940 --> 00:21:48,010
I hereby retract my prior statement.

260
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:51,380
Because that's what you demanded
of me.

261
00:21:57,020 --> 00:21:58,990
If I announce the video was faked,

262
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:00,820
what can you offer me, Dad?

263
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:02,760
Tell me what you want.

264
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:06,630
Give me the details
of your slush fund accounts.

265
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:07,760
What?

266
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:13,540
You think this nonsense can overturn
an official announcement?

267
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,710
She's out of her mind.

268
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:20,140
Get her out of here, now!

269
00:22:20,210 --> 00:22:22,380
Why do you think I would go so far
as to lie like that...

270
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,720
just to be your shield?

271
00:22:25,850 --> 00:22:28,090
It was all to lure you
into this very position.

272
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:32,260
To let your greed run wild.

273
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:36,030
That way,
when you reached the very top,

274
00:22:36,590 --> 00:22:39,400
I could be the one
to personally snap your leash.

275
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:43,470
You gave me far too much
to work with.

276
00:22:44,870 --> 00:22:46,040
It's too late to turn back now.

277
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,570
How dare you?

278
00:22:47,570 --> 00:22:49,540
Director Park!
Managing Director Jung!

279
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:51,980
Call security! Now!

280
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:54,510
You don't need security.
You need the police.

281
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:58,650
I got the doctor you bribed
to kill my mother...

282
00:22:59,150 --> 00:23:00,550
to confess.

283
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:03,620
A criminal complaint
has already been filed.

284
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:06,220
- This is too much.
- Se Hoon,

285
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:08,090
how did you get out?

286
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:10,290
And it was you who had me locked up
in a mental hospital,

287
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:12,060
wasn't it, Jin Tae Seok?

288
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,760
I told you, it was Gong Nan Sook!

289
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:17,000
Jin Tae Seok, you told me to do it!
Stop playing dumb!

290
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:19,370
- Is this too much?
- What on earth is going on...

291
00:23:23,410 --> 00:23:24,880
You've all lost your minds.

292
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:28,350
You're all in on it,
just dying to get rid of me.

293
00:23:29,050 --> 00:23:31,920
You think I'll let you
get away with this?

294
00:23:31,980 --> 00:23:35,020
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok.
Just stop.

295
00:23:35,490 --> 00:23:37,020
It's over for you now.

296
00:23:37,150 --> 00:23:38,320
It's over.

297
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:40,590
- It's time to step down.
- Get down from there!

298
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:46,900
(Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok's
Swiss Account Records Exposed)

299
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:50,130
If we don't distance ourselves now,
we're going down with him.

300
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:51,500
What do we do?

301
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,280
You're finished.

302
00:24:03,280 --> 00:24:04,280
Jin Tae Seok.

303
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:40,020
Let's meet.
I'll hand over everything I have.

304
00:24:40,780 --> 00:24:42,690
Meet me in the company parking lot
by 2pm.

305
00:24:49,890 --> 00:24:51,700
(Kunhyang Group)

306
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:56,800
(Kunhyang Group's Jin Tae Seok
Missing after Board Meeting Chaos)

307
00:24:58,370 --> 00:25:00,340
(Kunhyang Group's Jin Tae Seok
Indicted for Soliciting Murder)

308
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:09,050
Jin Tae Seok asked you to meet him?

309
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,320
He said he'd give me
everything he has.

310
00:25:13,950 --> 00:25:15,350
It's a trap to lure you in.

311
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:17,620
I'm sure it is.

312
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:19,260
I'll go instead.

313
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:20,390
No, it has to be me.

314
00:25:21,630 --> 00:25:23,230
This is my fate with Jin Tae Seok.

315
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:26,100
- It's a score I have to settle.
- No.

316
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,160
Jin Tae Seok is...

317
00:25:28,930 --> 00:25:30,300
my responsibility.

318
00:25:30,770 --> 00:25:33,670
Please, Mom.
Let me be the one to do it.

319
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,810
Please let me handle this my way.

320
00:25:37,670 --> 00:25:40,210
I'm so scared you'll get hurt again,
Jung Won.

321
00:25:40,410 --> 00:25:41,610
I'll be fine, Mom.

322
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:43,780
I'm not going to die.

323
00:25:46,850 --> 00:25:48,890
(Advisor Han Hye Ra)

324
00:25:52,090 --> 00:25:54,860
I have to protect my daughters,
even if it costs me my life.

325
00:25:56,460 --> 00:25:57,460
Jin Tae Seok...

326
00:25:58,930 --> 00:26:02,300
I have to end this,
once and for all.

327
00:26:05,770 --> 00:26:07,670
Is Jung Won going to meet
Jin Tae Seok?

328
00:26:08,370 --> 00:26:09,770
I couldn't stop her.

329
00:26:11,470 --> 00:26:12,580
She's in danger.

330
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:15,250
Go to Jung Won.

331
00:26:15,250 --> 00:26:17,110
I'll take care of Jin Tae Seok.

332
00:26:17,410 --> 00:26:18,420
What are you planning to do?

333
00:26:19,050 --> 00:26:20,050
I'm her mother.

334
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:22,350
This is about saving
my daughter's life.

335
00:26:23,190 --> 00:26:24,520
I'll do whatever it takes.

336
00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:20,380
Why do you want to come with me?

337
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:23,810
We can't just end things like this,
Tae Seok.

338
00:27:27,280 --> 00:27:28,620
You're trying to mess
with my head again.

339
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:32,990
Hye Ra, you despise me.

340
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:35,030
I despise you.

341
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:36,530
No...

342
00:27:38,060 --> 00:27:39,630
I despise myself even more.

343
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:47,740
If I hadn't chosen you,

344
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:52,540
none of this tragedy
would have ever happened.

345
00:27:54,810 --> 00:27:55,950
I'm the one who started this.

346
00:27:57,850 --> 00:28:00,020
My choices, my ambitions...

347
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:03,920
I accepted your obsession
and possessiveness.

348
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:07,690
This is the price I have to pay.

349
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:10,990
Hye Ra...

350
00:28:16,670 --> 00:28:18,170
I have to be the one to end this.

351
00:28:21,170 --> 00:28:22,210
What are you doing?

352
00:28:25,710 --> 00:28:27,680
- What are you doing?
- Let's end it here!

353
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:29,480
- Don't!
- Let go!

354
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:32,050
- Hye Ra, I said let go!
- Die with me!

355
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:39,560
(Under Construction)

356
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:09,020
(A Graceful Liar)

357
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:33,210
As Chairman of Kunhyang Group,
I'm the one to take the blame.

358
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:36,680
Joo Ha Neul leaked insider info,
and Chairman Gong funded illegal loans.

359
00:29:36,780 --> 00:29:38,920
What's going on with Chairman Joo?

360
00:29:39,150 --> 00:29:41,050
Joo Ha Neul, you're under arrest
for financial law violations...

361
00:29:41,050 --> 00:29:43,220
and fraudulent transactions
under the Capital Markets Act.

362
00:29:43,290 --> 00:29:44,720
Jin Tae Seok is dead.

363
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:46,360
This was your fate.

364
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:48,990
May you scream forever
in the depths of the abyss.

365
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:52,500
Jin Tae Seok, you're a dead man now,
and you will be forgotten.

366
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:57,070
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
